/A Business info system is needed to support ecommerce
/Which is the process of selling and distributing digital and physical goods in the online world
/A system is needed to set in place an organized methodology
/This can include everything from an inventory database to a CRM system
/Nowadays lots of data is seemingly stored in the cloud
/If you use a cloud server that processes or stores consumer information, security and encryption is an important topic
/An unsecure server may make a corporation liable if their ecommerce system gets hacked
'The better the encryption, the less monetary damage a hack causes
